\n34: ---\n35: \n36: ## 2. STATUS\n37: <!-- MACHINE-OWNED: START -->\n38: - Target: [from config.reviewTarget]\n39: - Target Type: [from config.reviewTargetType]\n40: - Started: [from config.createdAt]\n41: - Session: [from config.sessionId] (generation [from config.generation], lineage [from config.lineageMode])\n42: - Status: [ITERATING | CONVERGING | STUCK_RECOVERY | COMPLETE]\n43: - Release Readiness: [in-progress | converged | release-blocking]\n44: - Iteration: [N] of [maxIterations]\n45: - Provisional Verdict: [PASS | CONDITIONAL | FAIL | PENDING]\n46: - hasAdvisories: [true | false]\n47: <!-- MACHINE-OWNED: END -->\n48: \n49: ---\n50: \n51: ## 3. FINDINGS SUMMARY\n52: <!-- MACHINE-OWNED: START -->\n53: - **P0 (Critical):** [N] active, [N] new this iteration, [N] upgrades, [N] resolved\n54: - **P1 (Major):** [N] active, [N] new this iteration, [N] upgrades, [N] resolved\n55: - **P2 (Minor):** [N] active, [N] new this iteration, [N] upgrades, [N] resolved\n56: - **Repeated findings:** [N]\n57: - **Dimensions covered:** [correctness, security, traceability, maintainability]\n58: - **Convergence score:** [0.00-1.00]\n59: <!-- MACHINE-OWNED: END -->\n60: \n61: ---\n62: \n63: ## 4. PROGRESS\n64: <!-- MACHINE-OWNED: START -->\n65: \n66: | # | Focus | Files | Dimensions | New P0/P1/P2 | Ratio | Status |\n67: |---|-------|-------|------------|---------------|-------|--------|\n68: | [per iteration from JSONL] |\n69: <!-- MACHINE-OWNED: END -->\n70: \n71: ---\n72: \n73: ## 5. COVERAGE\n74: <!-- MACHINE-OWNED: START -->\n75: - Files reviewed: [X] / [Y] total\n76: - Dimensions complete: [X] / 4 total\n77: - Core protocols complete: [X] / [Y] required\n78: - Overlay protocols complete: [X] / [Y] applicable\n79: <!-- MACHINE-OWNED: END -->\n80: \n81: ---\n82: \n83: ## 6. TREND\n84: <!-- MACHINE-OWNED: START -->\n85: - Severity trend (last 3): [P0:N P1:N P2:N -> P0:N P1:N P2:N -> P0:N P1:N P2:N]\n86: - New findings trend (last 3): [N -> N -> N] [increasing | stable | decreasing]\n87: - Traceability trend (last 3): [pass/partial/fail counts -> ...]\n88: <!-- MACHINE-OWNED: END -->\n89: \n90: ---\n91: \n92: ## 7. RESOLVED / RULED OUT\n93: <!-- MACHINE-OWNED: START -->\n94: - **Disproved findings:** [findings investigated and determined to be false positives]\n95: - **Dead-end review paths:** [review approaches that yielded no actionable results]\n96: <!-- MACHINE-OWNED: END -->\n97: \n98: ---\n99: \n100: ## 8. NEXT FOCUS\n101: <!-- MACHINE-OWNED: START -->\n102: [from strategy.md \"Next Focus\" section, next dimension, file set, or review lens]\n103: <!-- MACHINE-OWNED: END -->\n104: \n105: ---\n106: \n107: ## 9. ACTIVE RISKS\n108: <!-- MACHINE-OWNED: START -->\n109: - [blockers, missing coverage, unresolved contradictions, gate violations, high stuck count, declining trend, etc.]\n110: <!-- MACHINE-OWNED: END -->\n111: \n112: ---\n113: \n114: ## 10. EXAMPLE (POPULATED)\n115: \n116: Reference snippet showing what a rendered review dashboard looks like after iteration 4 of a 7-iteration run. Use this as a visual anchor when inspecting a live dashboard.\n117: \n118: ```markdown\n119: # Deep Review Dashboard - Session Overview\n120: \n121: ## 2. STATUS\n122: - Target: .opencode/skills/deep-loop-workflows/deep-research (skill)\n123: - Started: 2026-04-21T10:02:11+02:00\n124: - Status: ITERATING\n125: - Iteration: 4 of 7\n126: - Verdict: PENDING\n127: - Coverage: core=pass, overlay=partial\n128: \n129: ## 3. PROGRESS\n130: \n131: | # | Dimension            | Files touched | P0 | P1 | P2 | Ratio | Status     |\n132: |---|----------------------|---------------|----|----|----|-------|------------|\n133: | 1 | correctness          | 8             | 0  | 3  | 4  | 0.78  | converged  |\n134: | 2 | test-coverage        | 6             | 1  | 2  | 1  | 0.52  | converging |\n135: | 3 | cross-runtime-parity | 5             | 0  | 2  | 0  | 0.41  | converging |\n136: | 4 | observability        | 4             | 0  | 1  | 2  | 0.29  | converging |\n137: \n138: ## 6. TRACEABILITY TREND\n139: - Core protocols: spec_code=pass, checklist_evidence=pass\n140: - Overlay protocols: skill_agent=pass, agent_cross_runtime=partial\n141: - Traceability trend (last 3): 3/0/1 -> 4/0/0 -> 4/1/0\n142: \n143: ## 9. ACTIVE RISKS\n144: - 1 P0 in test-coverage dimension -- review cannot terminate PASS until resolved\n145: - agent_cross_runtime protocol partial: Codex runtime path still unverified\n146: ```\n\n(End of file - total 146 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"---\ntitle: Deep Review Dashboard\ndescription: Auto-generated review session overview, refreshed after each iteration from JSONL state and strategy.\ntrigger_phrases:\n  - \"deep review dashboard\"\n  - \"review session overview\"\n  - \"review findings summary\"\n  - \"review coverage trend\"\nimportance_tier: normal\ncontextType: general\nversion: 1.11.0.15\n---\n\n# Deep Review Dashboard - Session Overview\n\nAuto-generated summary of the current review session, regenerated after every iteration evaluation from JSONL state and strategy. Never edited manually.\n\n## 1. OVERVIEW\n\n### Purpose","truncated":false,"loaded":[],"display":{"type":"file","path":"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/skills/deep-loop-workflows/deep-review/assets/deep_review_dashboard.md","text":"---\ntitle: Deep Review Dashboard\ndescription: Auto-generated review session overview, refreshed after each iteration from JSONL state and strategy.\ntrigger_phrases:\n  - \"deep review dashboard\"\n  - \"review session overview\"\n  - \"review findings summary\"\n  - \"review coverage trend\"\nimportance_tier: normal\ncontextType: general\nversion: 1.11.0.15\n---\n\n# Deep Review Dashboard - Session Overview\n\nAuto-generated summary of the current review session, regenerated after every iteration evaluation from JSONL state and strategy. Never edited manually.\n\n## 1. OVERVIEW\n\n### Purpose\n\nProvides a compact, human-readable summary of the current review session. Serves three roles:\n1. **Observability**, quick status check during long autonomous review runs\n2. **Recovery surface**, second recovery channel alongside JSONL after context compaction\n3. **Resume decision**, in confirm mode, shown to user before resume/restart choice\n\n### Usage\n\n- **Location:** `{artifact_dir}/deep-review-dashboard.md`\n- **Generated by:** Orchestrator (step_generate_dashboard in YAML workflow)\n- **Data sources:** `deep-review-state.jsonl` + `deep-review-strategy.md` + `deep-review-findings-registry.json`\n- **Protection:** `auto-generated`, overwritten each iteration, never manually edited\n\n---\n\n## 2. STATUS\n<!-- MACHINE-OWNED: START -->\n- Target: [from config.reviewTarget]\n- Target Type: [from config.reviewTargetType]\n- Started: [from config.createdAt]\n- Session: [from config.sessionId] (generation [from config.generation], lineage [from config.lineageMode])\n- Status: [ITERATING | CONVERGING | STUCK_RECOVERY | COMPLETE]\n- Release Readiness: [in-progress | converged | release-blocking]\n- Iteration: [N] of [maxIterations]\n- Provisional Verdict: [PASS | CONDITIONAL | FAIL | PENDING]\n- hasAdvisories: [true | false]\n<!-- MACHINE-OWNED: END -->\n\n---\n\n## 3. FINDINGS SUMMARY\n<!-- MACHINE-OWNED: START -->\n- **P0 (Critical):** [N] active, [N] new this iteration, [N] upgrades, [N] resolved\n- **P1 (Major):** [N] active, [N] new this iteration, [N] upgrades, [N] resolved\n- **P2 (Minor):** [N] active, [N] new this iteration, [N] upgrades, [N] resolved\n- **Repeated findings:** [N]\n- **Dimensions covered:** [correctness, security, traceability, maintainability]\n- **Convergence score:** [0.00-1.00]\n<!-- MACHINE-OWNED: END -->\n\n---\n\n## 4. PROGRESS\n<!-- MACHINE-OWNED: START -->\n\n| # | Focus | Files | Dimensions | New P0/P1/P2 | Ratio | Status |\n|---|-------|-------|------------|---------------|-------|--------|\n| [per iteration from JSONL] |\n<!-- MACHINE-OWNED: END -->\n\n---\n\n## 5. COVERAGE\n<!-- MACHINE-OWNED: START -->\n- Files reviewed: [X] / [Y] total\n- Dimensions complete: [X] / 4 total\n- Core protocols complete: [X] / [Y] required\n- Overlay protocols complete: [X] / [Y] applicable\n<!-- MACHINE-OWNED: END -->\n\n---\n\n## 6. TREND\n<!-- MACHINE-OWNED: START -->\n- Severity trend (last 3): [P0:N P1:N P2:N -> P0:N P1:N P2:N -> P0:N P1:N P2:N]\n- New findings trend (last 3): [N -> N -> N] [increasing | stable | decreasing]\n- Traceability trend (last 3): [pass/partial/fail counts -> ...]\n<!-- MACHINE-OWNED: END -->\n\n---\n\n## 7. RESOLVED / RULED OUT\n<!-- MACHINE-OWNED: START -->\n- **Disproved findings:** [findings investigated and determined to be false positives]\n- **Dead-end review paths:** [review approaches that yielded no actionable results]\n<!-- MACHINE-OWNED: END -->\n\n---\n\n## 8. NEXT FOCUS\n<!-- MACHINE-OWNED: START -->\n[from strategy.md \"Next Focus\" section, next dimension, file set, or review lens]\n<!-- MACHINE-OWNED: END -->\n\n---\n\n## 9. ACTIVE RISKS\n<!-- MACHINE-OWNED: START -->\n- [blockers, missing coverage, unresolved contradictions, gate violations, high stuck count, declining trend, etc.]\n<!-- MACHINE-OWNED: END -->\n\n---\n\n## 10. EXAMPLE (POPULATED)\n\nReference snippet showing what a rendered review dashboard looks like after iteration 4 of a 7-iteration run. Use this as a visual anchor when inspecting a live dashboard.\n\n```markdown\n# Deep Review Dashboard - Session Overview\n\n## 2. STATUS\n- Target: .opencode/skills/deep-loop-workflows/deep-research (skill)\n- Started: 2026-04-21T10:02:11+02:00\n- Status: ITERATING\n- Iteration: 4 of 7\n- Verdict: PENDING\n- Coverage: core=pass, overlay=partial\n\n## 3. PROGRESS\n\n| # | Dimension            | Files touched | P0 | P1 | P2 | Ratio | Status     |\n|---|----------------------|---------------|----|----|----|-------|------------|\n| 1 | correctness          | 8             | 0  | 3  | 4  | 0.78  | converged  |\n| 2 | test-coverage        | 6             | 1  | 2  | 1  | 0.52  | converging |\n| 3 | cross-runtime-parity | 5             | 0  | 2  | 0  | 0.41  | converging |\n| 4 | observability        | 4             | 0  | 1  | 2  | 0.29  | converging |\n\n## 6. TRACEABILITY TREND\n- Core protocols: spec_code=pass, checklist_evidence=pass\n- Overlay protocols: skill_agent=pass, agent_cross_runtime=partial\n- Traceability trend (last 3): 3/0/1 -> 4/0/0 -> 4/1/0\n\n## 9. ACTIVE RISKS\n- 1 P0 in test-coverage dimension -- review cannot terminate PASS until resolved\n- agent_cross_runtime protocol partial: Codex runtime path still unverified\n```","lineStart":1,"lineEnd":146,"totalLines":146,"truncated":false}},"title":".opencode/skills/deep-loop-workflows/deep-review/assets/deep_review_dashboard.md","time":{"start":1782210808748,"end":1782210808751}},"id":"prt_ef40aca01001XnYHptT3NkPNyU","sessionID":"ses_10bf585eeffeDIFj5xRNnSbPD5","messageID":"msg_ef40aa9f4001zwwVGi7RCCeWFl"}}
