he behavior] | [update/unchanged/not a consumer] | [grep/test/doc evidence] |\n101: | [consumer/status/docs/tests] | [how it observes the behavior] | [update/unchanged/not a consumer] | [grep/test/doc evidence] |\n102: \n103: Required inventories:\n104: - Same-class producers: `rg -n '<field|string|helper|literal|error-pattern>' <module-or-files>`.\n105: - Consumers of changed symbols: `rg -n '<changedSymbol>|<changedConstant>|<changedPublicField>' . --glob '*.ts' --glob '*.js' --glob '*.md'`.\n106: - Matrix axes: list every independent input axis and the required rows before implementation.\n107: - Algorithm invariant: for path/redaction/parser/resolver/security fixes, state the invariant and adversarial cases.\n108: <!-- /ANCHOR:affected-surfaces -->\n109: \n110: ---\n111: \n112: <!-- ANCHOR:phases -->\n113: ## 4. IMPLEMENTATION PHASES\n114: \n115: ### Phase 1: Setup\n116: - [ ] Project structure created\n117: - [ ] Dependencies installed\n118: - [ ] Development environment ready\n119: \n120: ### Phase 2: Core Implementation\n121: - [ ] [Core feature 1]\n122: - [ ] [Core feature 2]\n123: - [ ] [Core feature 3]\n124: \n125: ### Phase 3: Verification\n126: - [ ] Manual testing complete\n127: - [ ] Edge cases handled\n128: - [ ] Documentation updated\n129: <!-- /ANCHOR:phases -->\n130: \n131: ---\n132: \n133: <!-- ANCHOR:testing -->\n134: ## 5. TESTING STRATEGY\n135: \n136: | Test Type | Scope | Tools |\n137: |-----------|-------|-------|\n138: | Unit | [Components/functions] | [Jest/pytest/etc.] |\n139: | Integration | [API endpoints/flows] | [Tools] |\n140: | Manual | [User journeys] | Browser |\n141: <!-- /ANCHOR:testing -->\n142: \n143: ---\n144: \n145: <!-- ANCHOR:dependencies -->\n146: ## 6. DEPENDENCIES\n147: \n148: | Dependency | Type | Status | Impact if Blocked |\n149: |------------|------|--------|-------------------|\n150: | [System/Library] | [Internal/External] | [Green/Yellow/Red] | [Impact] |\n151: <!-- /ANCHOR:dependencies -->\n152: \n153: ---\n154: 